overview.en: LINC chain, based on the characteristics of non-tampering and decentralization of block chain data, can effectively solve the cashed-in application of various commercial fields around the world. The value of LINC is reflected in its own technical strength, ecological application range, constant circulation, market consensus and a series of high-quality labels.LINC chain will build up a diversified and global comprehensive group. In the future, it will focus on block chain technology, vigorously develop digital industry, and develop global business in the form of offline + online + whole industrial chain, providing strong support for the development of LINC chain.
overview.zh: LINC链，基于区块链数据不可篡改和去中心化等特质，其诞生，便可有效解决全球各种商业领域的兑现应用，LINC的价值体现在其本身的技术实力、生态应用范围、恒定发行量、市场共识度等一系列优质标签。LINC链将构建起一个多元化、全球化的综合性集团，未来将全力聚焦区块链技术，大力发展数字产业，以线下+线上+链上全产业链的形式发展全球业务，为LINC链的发展提供强大的支持。
